events.description:
# Shwoop HQ

 Come through to the Unleash Space and say "Hi!" to our team. To redeem prizes, or ask question just look out for our volunteers in Shwoop Merch.

![the market banner](https://uoa-bs-maps.s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/The-Market-Logo.png)
# $500 The Market Gift Card

Take 15 seconds to enter your details and go in the draw to win a $500 shopping spree from The Market

[Follow This Link To The Market](https://themarket.com/about/aut-shwoop/?utm_source=aut_shwoop&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=500_dollar_giveaway&fbclid=IwAR1-_eVh9CqwZqrYgmH0coVAt44cCQQ8Iw3SJ01Bo00kgSwQTDxmNoQZrXs)

# Shwoop Facebook

 Message us using our Facebook. Also available in the About page in the menu. [Follow This Link For Our Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/shwoopnz)

# More Shwoop?!

We’re continuing next week at The Faculty of Science Buildings all week long! That’s RIGHT - YOU GET EVEN MORE FREE STUFF! We also have a super challenge where the winner gets $1,000 to go towards your Uni Fees for a Science Paper including GenEds.

# Feedback

Hey guys, we’re a tiny little startup and we want to come back next time with a much larger prize pool. It would mean the world if you could please rate us on the store.

text:
We’re situated in the Unleash Space for just today, come here to get your first prize!

Make sure Bluetooth and location is turned on and get close to the Shwoop tile. If your phone isn’t working, try restarting the app and ensure it is up to date.

Watch me shake
Hear me grind.
Now you wake
Peace of mind. 
Exams are near
Answer is clear
Adventure to isle
It’s worthwhile
But not at Kate Edgar
Somewhere near here...

A prize icon will be displayed instead of this marker when completed. All food and beverages must be redeemed after 1PM. You can redeem food and beverages until the end of exams.

Go around the corner and send us a photo on Messenger of where the Purple Lime is and get in range of our beacon. Remember, please park your Limes in the designated areas such as this one and other purple Lime locations. Unique codes must be redeemed by today.

If you don’t have Lime, use promo code “Shwoop” to get an extra $5. Tap the pink marker next to this one to get our messenger link.

First woman in our nation with a degree,
Now a location you will often see,
A place to snack, kickback, and cram
Here at the bottom, ready for exams.

TheMarket voucher must be redeemed by this Saturday night. Please message us on Messenger if it doesn’t work.

We print your student IDs,
And answer questions for free ,
If you’re looking for information ,
You’ve come to the right station.
Go visit the ATM at the Quad to get this. This marker is on the exact coordinates.

Beds of flowers grow South of the speaker's post,
Victorias street West of my post,
In the centre a fountain great and wide,
The Pavillion is where your treasure resides.
